data.description:
Huge Price improvement!!   This spacious and inviting one-level home offers a comfortable and luxurious living experience in the prestigious Ridgefields neighborhood. With 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and an impressive 2,700 square feet of living space, this property boasts numerous amenities that make it an ideal  home.
As you enter the home, you'll immediately notice the open and airy layout. The living area is generously sized and flows seamlessly into the dining and kitchen areas. 
The kitchen is a chef's dream, with modern appliances, ample counter space, and plenty of storage in the cabinetry. It's perfect for preparing delicious meals and entertaining guests.
The master bedroom is a tranquil retreat, complete with its own  bathroom, and French doors that open to back patio. Additionally, there are three more spacious bedrooms, one of which also includes built-in bookshelves and a desk. The bonus room can serve as a versatile space, ideal for use as a mother-in-law suite, a playroom, or a home office.
The highlight of this property is the screened-in patio that overlooks the beautiful .73-acre lot. You can enjoy the stunning views of Bays Mountain while relaxing in this comfortable outdoor space. On hot summer days, take a dip in the 8-foot inground pool.
The home is equipped with thermo-safe windows installed in 2009,  updated HVAC unit with a 1 year warranty, leaf gutter guards and  it has also been freshly painted and features new flooring, providing a modern and updated feel.
Located in the desirable Ridgefields neighborhood, this home offers easy access to excellent schools, shopping centers, and recreational activities like hiking and fishing. Whether you're a looking for a spacious and convenient place to call home or seeking a peaceful and picturesque retreat, this property offers it all. Call a Realtor today for your private showing!!!
